'''Iẓi'''<ref>https://amawal.net/i%E1%BA%93i</ref> (s [[Tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]] : ⵉⵥⵉ, s [[Tutlayt Taɛṛabt|tasrɣint]] : المرارة, s [[Tutlayt Tafransist|tfṛansist]] : Vésicule biliaire) iga yan usknaf imẓẓin, ixwan sg ugnsu. Ar gis ittmunu yan uḥruray<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref> igan awraɣ ([[Aḥruray awraɣ]]) urta iddi s ilawin (nɣ ilawan nɣ iẓṛman) imẓẓayn n [[Afgan|ufgan]]<ref>https://ar.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D9%85%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A9</ref>.

Illa iẓi g izddar n [[Tasa]], ar d ittacka uḥruray awraɣ sg tasa s iẓi, ar gis ittmunu ilmma iddu s ilawin imẓẓayn bac ad yaws g ubṭṭu n tafrdeddist<ref>https://tal.ircam.ma/dglai/lexieam.php</ref>.

